>>__ Parse.temp_set_grammars $ valOf $ grammarDB {thyname="hol"};
## `is_gen_tyvar`

``` hol4
Type.is_gen_tyvar : hol_type -> bool
```

------------------------------------------------------------------------

Checks if a type variable has been created by `gen_tyvar`.

### Failure

Never fails.

### Example

``` hol4
>> is_gen_tyvar (gen_tyvar());

>> is_gen_tyvar bool;
```

### See also

[`Type.gen_tyvar`](#Type.gen_tyvar)
